\id 1TH  
\h 1 TESALONIKA 
\toc1 1 Tesalonika 
\toc2 1 Tesalonika 
\toc3 1 Tesalonika 
\mt1 1 Tesalonika  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Pol, Sailas, Timoti,  
\p amã, Tesalonika sios Tamada Negur, Odug Jesus Kristus ado bun ufaregef ã bun, pas enei matotof:  
\p Wau ifenẽya wau inosiya ado ã bun ibodõf.   
\s1 Tesalonika Neid Momoiya Nigin De Fiyẽya  
\p
\v 2 Amã faimud ã ganan nigin Negur de mafiye ken, nemã kosẽ bun ã nigin marokenẽdig.  
\v 3 Amã neda Negur Tamada mala bun, momoiya bunem ãgenei kabĩ faat yuk, wauĩ laa fiya bunem ãgenei kabĩ yaleya ado, neda Odug Jesus Kristus bun wauĩ ise fen, ã to fese gen anĩ toku karĩ mauledig.   
\p
\v 4 Turamã tar, Negur ã nigin wau laa fedig anĩ, amã keleĩ, are Negur ĩ ã igirnein,  
\v 5 ere nigin, nemã biya od ã bun isin, are od dogol bunem sã, anĩ ere, megeir ado, Awa Uur Fateul ado, momoiya bagai ado, ã bun isin. Ã atun, ã nigin naig be ma mabodon anĩ ã keleĩ.  
\v 6 Ã, amã Odug Jesus geid madẽ wamãgen. Ã darau odug adon, anĩ ere, Awa Uur Fateulem kulĩya ifenein anĩ bun, ã od anĩ walegen.  
\v 7 Anĩ nigin, ã Masedonia Akaia provins ado bun, momoiya tamo kayau ganan neid dodo gen wowã gen.  
\v 8 Odug nẽ od ã bunem ilen, Masedonia Akaia provins ado bun dogol sã, ãgenei Negur nigin momoiya anĩ fõ fõ ganan iyokelen. Anĩ nigin amã baban ã ereb to mayeĩf.  
\v 9 Idi dogo, ã amã naig ge walemãgen anĩ kurõ difalaisi kanamak. Age de fen, ã naig ge idegẽya waitou utorõg fen, Negur bun falei ge, mata ibodõya nẽ ado momoi nẽ Negur aruna waleg fen,  
\v 10 ĩ Naal ĩ laa bunem turĩ fiyen, are Jesus ĩ didi dumen isiyouf bun tamal kel yaledadig anĩ, saa ilun tamal tari gen anĩ dirokanamak.   
\c 2  
\s1 Pol Tesalonika Oun Kabĩ Yalen  
\p
\v 1 Turamã tar, ã keleĩ, amã nemã ki yeĩya ege to ilen.  
\v 2 Ã keleĩ, amã Filipai taun oun darau ado kono fiya malen, anĩ ere, neda Negur nẽ isennẽya bunem amã totol mano fen, naabura gudũ fiya totol ibod mog, in biya od wogõ mayein.  
\v 3 Amã totol bagai marokeneik are, kũ fenẽya bunem sã, kisi sane bunem sã, idegneĩya bunemeg sã.  
\v 4 Age fiya ban, Negur biya od wogõya nigin igirneĩd fen, yo fiyẽdin anidim gen, amã wogõ maudig. Amã tamo waud al fouf nigin to kabĩ malef, anĩ ere, Negur ĩ wauda es fedig, ĩ wau al fouf nigin kabĩ malef.  
\v 5 Ã keleĩ, amã meleĩ yaleya nigin to bagai wogõ mau fen, naumamã nigin to nawamã dede mafedig. Are amã momoi morok anĩ Negur ĩ keleĩ.  
\v 6 Amã tamom yanamã seli kulõ difouf nigin to mamiren, ã bunem sã, taka bunemeg sã.  
\p Amã Kristus nẽ aposel mau fen, amã sã morõ mafeneĩ yoũ nẽ,  
\v 7 anĩ ere, ã atun, amã molol nem kesu sina gere tar kulatun fedidig gen, age mafen.  
\v 8 Amã ã nigin waumã fatuk laaf fen, amã Negur nẽ biya od ifeneĩya nigin dogol sã, nemã mata ã nigin iraileya nigineg waumã iron, ere nigin, ã amã bun oboimã bagai wowã gen.  
\v 9 Turamã tar, momoi, amã kabĩ totol morõ ado malen anĩ ã karĩ welegef. Amã morõ ã taka to mafeneĩf nigin, bõ ado gaa ado kabĩ male fen, Negur nẽ biya od ã bun wogõ maun.   
\p
\v 10 Ã, momoiya tamo atun, amã naig be mafen, fateul, madur bagai, od sã mafaren, are ã keleĩ, Negureg keleĩ.  
\v 11 Ã keleĩ, are amã, tama ĩ gere tar nigin suma inodig gen, ã mugu mugu bun suma manon,  
\v 12 amã wauĩ malesedig, wowor mayeĩdig, Negur ĩ yogon tano ado fula fiya medeĩya bun ulagauf nigin iweigneik, ĩ orof kilei ã ubodõgouf nigin, wedereĩ maroudig.   
\p
\v 13 Age ma fen, amãg toku Negur de mafiyẽdig, ere nigin, sain ã Negur nẽ od amã bunem karĩg fen, walegen, are tamo nẽ od gen to walegen, Negur nẽ od bagai walegen, Negur nẽ od anĩ, momoi gef ã bun kabĩ yalef.  
\v 14 Turamã tar, ã oun Judia distrik Negur nẽ sios madẽ wiyẽdigen. Sios Judia distrik oun Kristus Jesus bun difaref, Juda tamo bun darau dalen gen bagai, ãg fõ tureĩ tar bun darau walegen.  
\v 15 Juda tamo idi, Odug Jesus profet geid didenkeis fen, amãg dirumã dirailen. Idi Negur wau al fiya to difenen, idi tamo ganan kiwai difenẽdif.  
\v 16 Idi neid tobonuneid bun, amã haiden wogõ mafiyẽdi di, isennẽya dalouf nigin naaburamã gudũ difedig. Naab anĩ bunem, faimud idi neid mosor tete tete dife di, mudu isedig. Age fiya nigin, Negur nẽ didi kisi feleya bagai, idi bun mogo isin.   
\s1 Pol Tesalonika Ileya Nigin Fatuk Bagai Wau Iron  
\p
\v 17 Anĩ ere, turamã tar, sain modeg bun, ã geid tabodon anĩ fara mafen (are bouwamam, kisim sã), amã ã ileyeĩya nigin fatuk bagai waumã iro ken, naab ganan bun kabĩ totol malen.  
\v 18 Amã ã gein masiyouf nigin waumã yenen. Momoi, aya, Pol, baba baban lakĩ afen. Anĩ ere, Satan naaburamã katĩ felen.  
\v 19 Neda Odug Jesus isiyouf bun, ere anĩ ĩ mala bun, nemã wau iseya, kulĩya, yana yaleseya nẽ teter youf? Are ã anĩ sã de?  
\v 20 Momoi, ã nemã fula fiya medeĩya ado, nemã kulĩya.   
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ nigin, amã foiya kisi feleya sã nigin, amã kisi ma fen, amã mugu ein Atens mabodõf are deuf maun.  
\v 2 Amã, ã ãgenei momoiya bun megeir yei ken, wauĩ yalesauf nigin, Timoti, ĩ nemã turamã ado Kristus nẽ biya od nigin Negur nẽ kabĩ tura, sur mafiyen.  
\v 3 Are takam morõ eneidi bun to kisi rori youf nigin age mafen. Ã gai keleĩ bagai, are ada morõ eneidi nigin igirnadan.  
\v 4 Momoi, amã ã geid tabodon bun, amã, ada fau darau difanadauf nigin toku marokenein. Age fiya bagai, agef wõ yen, are ã keleĩ.  
\v 5 Anĩ nigin, aya foiya kisi feleya sã kisi afe fen, aya ãgenei momoiya ileya nigin sur afen. Aya, naab taka taka bun kisi fiya tamo kisi yeĩ di, nemã kabĩ totol ege ileya nigin kumĩ aun.   
\s1 Timotim Pol Od Biya Iroulekenen  
\p
\v 6 Anĩ ere, Timoti gama bagai, ã bun tamal amã gein isi fen, ãgenei momoiya ado wauĩ laa fiya nigin od biya irou isin. Ĩ irokanaman, are ã, amã nigin faimud biya karĩ welegedig ado, amã ã ileyeĩya nigin waumã irõdig gen, ãg ilemãya nigin wauĩ irõdig yen.  
\v 7 Anĩ nigin, turamã tar, amã nemã waumã morõ ado, darau ganan bun, ãgenei momoiya bunem, amã ã nigin waumã yalesen.  
\v 8 Gama amã waumã kulĩya ado mata mabodok, ere nigin, ã Odug bun megeir ufaregef.  
\v 9 Neda Negur mala bun, amã ã nigin waumã kulĩya ifanaman enei ganan nigin, naig ma abag kisi mafel, ã nigin Negur de mafiyẽf?  
\v 10 Amã masi mailiyei ken, ereb ã fau ãgenei momoiya bun lau gef anĩ isenneĩya nigin, bõ ado gaa ado Negur totol bagai kosẽ mafiyẽdig.   
\p
\v 11 Gama, neda Negur Tamada ĩ yogo, neda Odug Jesus ado, nemã naab ã gein isiya nigin dũf nigin oromak.  
\v 12 Odug ãgenei wauĩ laa fiya gire fese di, amã ã nigin waumã laa fedig age fiya gen, abob nigin ado ganan nigin wauĩ laa fiya gogũ fouf nigin oromak.  
\v 13 Negur ĩ, ãgenei wauĩ megeir fe di, neda Odug Jesus, in fateul tamo kayau ganan geid disiyouf sain bun, neda Negur Tamada mala bun, ã bouweĩ od sã fateul wõ gouf nigin oromak.   
\c 4  
\s1 Mata Ibodõya Bun Negur Wau Al Fiya Ifenẽya  
\p
\v 1 Od idĩya nigin, turamã tar, amã, ã Negur wau al fiya wenẽgouf nigin naig ge ufaragauf nigin mafelnein, are gama agog ufaregef. Gama amã ã enei baba baban ago gouf nigin to mayei ken, Odug Jesus bun totol bagai marokeneik.  
\v 2 Odug Jesus nẽ totol bunem, amã ã faded fiya mafenein, are ã keleĩ.   
\p
\v 3 Negur nẽ oroya are ã fateul wowã gouf anĩ, are ã noli tobonunã sese wiyẽgouf.  
\v 4 Ã mugu mugu bouweĩ kulatun ge di, fateul fen, yeneĩ biyauf nigin keleĩ youf.  
\v 5 Haiden Negur keleĩ sam, noli nigin mudureid ditenẽdig gen to ago gouf.  
\v 6 Enei bun, takam ne tura sane to age fiyẽf, idegẽya bunem morõ to ifenẽf. Amã mogo marokenei ken, wedereĩ maroun, are Odug fau mosor age fediya ganan nigin tamo mala solo ifenẽdiyouf.  
\v 7 Negur ada amuyẽ adouf nigin to iweignadan, anĩ ere, fateul ibodõya nigin iweignadan.  
\v 8 Anĩ nigin, taka ĩ od enei idodõf, ĩ tamo to idodnek, are Negur in Awa Uur Fateul ifeneĩdig anĩ idodnek.   
\p
\v 9 Gama tureĩ tar nigin wauĩ laa fiya anĩ nigin amã to matotkeneĩf, ere nigin, ã aug abob nigin wauĩ laa fouf nigin Negurem ifelnein.  
\v 10 Momoi, ã tureĩ tar ganan Masedonia provins ganan bun difaref anidi nigin wauĩ laa fedig. Anĩ ere, turamã tar, ã baba baban ago gouf nigin totol bagai marokeneik.   
\p
\v 11 Amã marokenein gen, ã molol ibodõya nigin kisi totol walogouf, ãgenei kabĩ nigin kisig fen, aug imeim kabĩ walogouf.  
\v 12 Anĩ bunem, ãgenei ibodõya bun tamo serẽ temeleid dileyei ken, anini douf, taka bun to utobõgouf.   
\s1 Odug Isiyouf  
\p
\v 13 Turamã tar, amã ã gare den onudi nigin to keleĩ youf anĩ to oromak, takag, tamo tunĩ ganan, wau iseya sã gen wauĩ gudũ fouf anĩ to oromak.  
\v 14 Jesus laaf fen, kel fã yen nigin ada momoi tauf, anĩ nigin, Negur, idi Jesus bun gare den anidi, Jesus geid guri feid isiyouf nigin momoi tauf.  
\v 15 Odug nẽ od bunem, amã ã marokeneik, are ada fau mata tabodok, Odug isiyouf bun tafaref ada, idi gare den anidi to bagai wal tafediyouf.  
\v 16 Odug yogo bagai saa ilunem isiyouf, ait odugem irõ di, engel uyu irouya nẽ ait ado, Negur nẽ taur bunem iweig di, Kristus bun gare den anidi ketem fafã douf.  
\v 17 Anĩ bure fele di, ada fau mata tabod ken, tafaref anĩ geif, idi geid bagu fada fen, lalo bun kutũ fada se, Odug fotou fiya nigin saa ilun irou iselnadauf. An ada Odug geid mata gai gai tabodkalauf.  
\v 18 Anĩ nigin, od enei bunem abob wau talesauf.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Gama, turamã tar, amã sain ado naa nigin to matotkeneĩf.  
\v 2 Ere nigin, ã keleĩ bagai, Odug nẽ naa, bẽ tamo bõ isiyouf gen wõ youf.  
\v 3 Tamo kayau wau inosiya ado morõ sã tabodok de mog, daũ fiya nunũ idi bun, kayau kesu gõ fiya nigin firi yedig gen isi di, idi to diyalalauf.   
\p
\v 4 Anĩ ere, turamã tar, ã gugum bun to ufaregef, anĩ nigin, naa anĩ bẽ tamo gen to isi fen, ba yeĩf.  
\v 5 Ã ganan lalan ado we bun temeleĩ. Ada bõ ado gugum nẽ sã.  
\v 6 Anĩ nigin, ada, idi tunĩ denek gen to tafarauf, anĩ ere, ada lo tafel fen, karĩ adouf.  
\v 7 Are idi mulaĩ temeleid, bõ anĩ denẽdig, idi aai meleid waĩ yedig, bõ anĩ aai meleid waĩ yedig.  
\v 8 Anĩ ere, ada we nẽ nigin, ada dug nigin karĩ ado fen, momoiya wau laa fiya ado siot kapa gen tafoun ken, kel gei fiya nẽ wau iseya anim hat kapa gen kurũ tafouf.  
\v 9 Negur ada didi yaleya nigin to igirnadan, anĩ ere, ada neda Odug Jesus Kristus bunem kel gei fadauf nigin igirnadan.  
\v 10 Ĩ ada nigin laa fen, are ada mata be tabodok, gare be tauf are, ĩ geid tabodõf nigin age fen.  
\v 11 Anĩ nigin, abob wau tales fen, abob walesagauf, gama ago gef gen.   
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Faded Fiya  
\p
\v 12 Turamã tar, gama amã marokeneik, idi ã atun kabĩ totol dalef, idi Odug bun ãgenei uyu irouya difar fen, wedereĩ dirouf anidi karĩ wiyẽdigouf.  
\v 13 Idi kabĩ dirouf nigin ge fen, idi nigin wauĩ laaf fen, fatuk bagai karĩ wiyẽdigouf. Abob nigin wau inosiya bun ufaragauf.  
\v 14 Turamã tar, amã totol bagai marokeneik, fõ temeleid wedereid uroug, anini temeleid waud waleseg fen, forõ temeleid usennẽdigouf, ganan nigin nameĩ ukeleg ubodõgouf.  
\v 15 Taka nem taka nẽ mosor to solo fouf, anĩ ere, abob nigin ado ganan nigin, faimud tobonunã biya ago gouf.   
\p
\v 16 Wauĩ bun faimud kulĩ youf,  
\v 17 toku kosẽ gouf,  
\v 18 ereb ereb ganan bun de wiyẽgouf, ere nigin, are ã nigin Kristus Jesus bun Negur nẽ oroya.   
\p
\v 19 Awa Uur nẽ yã to uroroukeleg,  
\v 20 profet neid od to welebi ge.  
\v 21 Ereb ereb ganan es gouf. Biya anĩ uroug, kafĩ walagauf.  
\v 22 Ereb sesen fire fire ganan sese gouf.   
\p
\v 23 Negur ĩ yogo, wau inosiya nẽ Negur, fateul kisi feleya bagai inoyeĩf. Ãgenei uur, meleĩkanon ado, bouweĩ anĩ ganan, neda Odug Jesus Kristus isiyouf bun od sãf.  
\v 24 Ĩ iweigneik ĩ yogon od dõ fiya biya, ĩ de age fouf.   
\p
\v 25 Turamã tar, amã nigin kosẽg.  
\v 26 Tureĩ tar ganan, umã fiya fateul bunem aan wedig.  
\v 27 Aya, tureĩ tar ganan bun pas enei uwesagauf nigin, Odug mala bun totol bagai arokeneik.   
\p
\v 28 Neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ wau ifenẽya ã ado ibodõf.   